{
  "stem": "24111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to-- we were understood strict carabinieri, which is the police, control.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they supported, actually, financially, partially, while the rest was supported by the-- by the Italian Jewish community, by the DELASEM.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we had suddenly to-- to leave Villa Emma, before we had to do that, Joschko went to the priests and Dr.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bocari and asked them if they-- if-- the existing cloister in Nonantola is a big cloister, for nuns and for novices but only for girls-- if they would take in the children.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after a little bartering, they say, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We take all children, girls, and my mother, a-- a woman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we take you if you take the priest-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] abbot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you can stay with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we don't take the boys, the-- the teenage boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took only the boys up to, I believe, 14-- or perhaps-- up till 14.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the bigger boys, they couldn't take.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they had only an woman close-there-- cloister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had a lot of girl novices and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't-- they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the farmers in Nonantola and surrounding, they were told, by the priest, take the boys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we took shelter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we got shelter, with the farmers of Nonantola.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] His name is in the Yad Vashem in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they planted trees in his name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got recognition as one of the 'Righteous Ones.' And if you give me a few moments, I will remember.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But right now, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he and Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bocari were brought to Israel after the war in, I think, '85.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were bestowed the honor of the 'Righteous People.' And trees were planted in-- in his name.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
